hosting_settings.description:
 Fields depend on the `hosting_type` value:
for `virtual`:
`ftp_login` - FTP user login name (required when creating a subscription). `ftp_password` - FTP user password (required when creating a subscription). `www_root` - WWW root directory for the domain (optional, defaults to the domain name).
for `standard_forwarding`:
`dest_url` - URL to redirect the visitor to (required). `http_code` - HTTP redirect code; allowed values: `301`, `302` (optional, defaults to `301`).
for `frame_forwarding`:
`dest_url` - URL to load inside the frame (required).
for `none`: no fields are expected.

